race.description: Tabtouch - Have You Got The Touch Handicap
race.comment: TAKE A LEAF (10) finished off strongly to pick up the victory at this track and trip a fortnight ago, running away to win by 1.2L. Faithfull replaces the apprentice hoop and it wouldn't surprise to see her take closer order from an inside barrier. Looks a nice type on the rise and can continue her winning ways. KIDDING ME (8) got over the top to score in a photo finish at Geraldton last time out, breaking her maiden. This is tougher, but she turned in a good figure there and the rise in trip looks to suit. Can lob in a handy position and bring up back-to-back wins. GOD'S GRIN (7) is another who scored in a photo finish, jumping a $1.45 favourite and knocking over the maiden. Has the speed to roll forward from a tricky barrier and can play a leading role if she can hold her form. RIVER ANGEL (6) is better than we saw last time out and can improve today out in distance. JAZALOT (2) can improve second-up and out in trip.
